# non-goals
# - drop-in ghostty replacement (we will diverge in UX)
# - being a shell (void drives shells, does not replace them)

# operational notes (2026-04-22)
# - CI: gh api push must be used for .github/workflows/* (TCC denies local
#   writes to those paths). Same for install.hexa.
# - Local checkout to /Applications/Void.app: `ditto` always fails on
#   shell-integration/bash/bash-preexec.sh with "Operation not permitted"
#   but the overwrite succeeds for the rest of the bundle. Not a blocker.
# - Namespace runners don't work on this fork — Test.yml runs pend forever
